          +p("ne of my life goals is to leave everything I come in contact with better than I found it. ")
          +link({
            href: "/my-resume",
            class: "layout-margin-vert-dull layout-margin-left-mini"
          })(data-swup-preload itemprop="url")
            span(itemprop="name") my resume.
